    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_ce3331b6-a3d4-4f8f-94e5-50fd60e44728" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When your students start a quiz, their attempt is tied to the version of the quiz at the time they started. If you make any updates to the quiz after a student after a student begins taking the quiz, those updates will not be available to the student during their current attempt. We recommend not publishing a quiz or making it available to students until all changes have been made. However, if you need to make changes while a student is currently taking the quiz, the student must end their current attempt and you need to moderate the quiz and give them another attempt with the updated quiz.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-quizzes" data-step-uuid="082e7ba0-55f0-4817-b008-4baf2564004d">
    <h2 id="open-quizzes" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Quizzes</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/272/264/original/3b1937d1-e2a7-442f-933d-eefe236dafd0.png" srcset="" alt="Open Quizzes" height="332" width="174">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_e9633abd-1a30-4658-a3df-9abdf547a4cc" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Quizzes</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-quiz" data-step-uuid="c4ec0e66-d7ab-4eb2-b1ab-902b950a182f">
    <h2 id="open-quiz" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Quiz</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/272/266/original/09dcaaf1-b633-452f-bf20-d3edf4ffa7a3.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/272/266/medium/09dcaaf1-b633-452f-bf20-d3edf4ffa7a3.png" srcset="" alt="Open Quiz" height="151" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1ba28f17-7538-4c83-a858-5b7a65ff3242" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the title of the quiz you need to moderate.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="moderate-quiz" data-step-uuid="e427ccfe-72b3-4c53-a362-f5c73e7a6dc4">
    <h2 id="moderate-quiz" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Moderate Quiz</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/278/657/original/914b287d-2301-426c-9a9d-1dbe31156f7e.png" srcset="" alt="Moderate Quiz" height="192" width="276">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_4ee9b865-d66b-4948-809c-0e1f1b6d3b8c" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To moderate the quiz, click the <strong>Moderate This Quiz</strong> link. On the Moderate Quiz page, you can <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/docs/DOC-13076-415250753" target="_blank">give the student an extra attempt</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="ask-student-to-submit-quiz" data-step-uuid="9762b4ea-e48b-412a-a8ec-e87dc54ffeff">
    <h2 id="ask-student-to-submit-quiz" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Ask Student to Submit Quiz</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/046/786/original/7b1d3d72-4c1d-4716-9365-5e396be9516e.png" srcset="" alt="Ask Student to Submit Quiz" height="670" width="677">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_14a58f2f-77c0-474e-a27a-7ed2038b7330" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Contact the student who is currently taking the quiz and ask them to submit the quiz [1]. If they haven't finished the quiz, they will need to confirm their incomplete submission [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="prevent-quiz-access" data-step-uuid="964fe3dd-4e29-454f-a04e-81c0a34f1274">
    <h2 id="prevent-quiz-access" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Prevent Quiz Access</h2>
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3c8bcb1f-f168-4868-b055-4a2e98d18f92" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To prevent students from accessing quizzes before they are complete, you can: </p>
<ul>
<li>Leave the quiz unpublished in the course until complete, or place the quiz in an unpublished module. </li>
<li>Use <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/docs/DOC-9959-415250754" target="_blank">availability dates in quiz settings</a> to prevent students from accessing the quiz until a specific date.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
